text: MAGIMA mahmmia, waj KNOWTRE that they called us 10 more to adopt practices that are anticipated to have a positive impact on their business, such as vaccination. To change this, a checklist was developed jointly with County and National Veterinary Services with priority biosecurity practices that could lead to the reduction of emerging zoonotic diseases such as salmonella and to mitigate antimicrobial resistance. Awa hajiwa kutim functioni, yaazwa kuhuwa kuhuwa kuhuwa kuhuwa. Kuwa hula, kukili, kuka mambwa ya usafi. Wili Сjibut na Nifakwa. Wili Nifakwa kua wa kukasa. Kukusha kwa wili Nifakwa kuzi, kuzi osha. Miu mediki Fika ninawa kumbusha. Wili Nifakwa. Kuka mambwa wa meleha. Tambawii na tusaidiya. Kutuwa nyonsha patikilale. К Kuqaakaf0... K mindsirbatsuun upupawa kwa sayidiasana, ko sababu hatu kwa tunajua kuna kaini area and dati area. Tata kwa traini, tunaseparati feyalans And kakasis kira ki tu kinaida separiti re. Ata traini tuba tiba ratifiki, atrisdi imimbufukasi etu Tuna pata kasi mingiki kudiku kakuni ya kutuna pata paradi. We are training we have been reduced mortalities in their crops. The barns also gain the swatter which faster. And this gives them good money. Kwa kwa gafani kwa the poultry valuation business in Kenya, there exist notable gaps the those there but the ammunition has not been very good. Fisha tugeoba wachi jajiote wa patehi elimu hiri wachi jaji na usafi wa kuku ukuesawa.
